{"tid":2437735,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"立法會選舉再押後？林鄭：呢刻唔能夠講畀大家聽","createTime":"2021-03-08T05:12:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T05:34:26.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d938c82e98466a1f14615a2e85e18195eec46781","tid":2437735,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:12:40.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥中午舉行記者會，回應人大改選舉制度。她拒絕確認，原本已押後一年、原定於今年 9 月舉行的立法會選舉，會否再次押後。她解釋，「呢刻唔能夠講畀大家聽，係咪一定再次押後（立法會）選舉。」<br />\n<br />\n她提到，根據人大修改選舉制度的草案，選舉委員會被賦予新的職權，會透過選舉產生較大比例立法會議員，「邏輯上來講，應是選舉委員會選舉（原定 2021年12月）先舉行，然後到第 7 屆立法會選舉。」<br />\n<br />\n選舉委員會原定在今年 12 月舉行，但林鄭稱選委會的選舉日期「不一定是一成不變」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/156661378_3962482267170697_4225502247104456904_n.png?_nc_cat=100&amp;ccb=1-3&amp;_nc_sid=973b4a&amp;_nc_ohc=S7iHIUyvWAwAX8bN98A&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-1.xx&amp;oh=686a931c1eb00d810263e665fd42a26e&amp;oe=606B89B1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F156661378_3962482267170697_4225502247104456904_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26ccb%3D1-3%26_nc_sid%3D973b4a%26_nc_ohc%3DS7iHIUyvWAwAX8bN98A%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg4-1.xx%26oh%3D686a931c1eb00d810263e665fd42a26e%26oe%3D606B89B1&h=482c65dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3962482263837364/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.720050934747196%2F3962482263837364%2F&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058q7XYz%2BrpCtmef%2B4BlhZTRs%3D&h=d0d58c1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3962482263837364/</a>"},{"pid":"5e3ea2607ce747d5788c7dac684674d88fbc0c61","tid":2437735,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T05:15:09.000Z","msg":"而家支那比呢隻支那狗既稿真係愈來愈少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經係棄卒，但讀稿既內容都少咗好多"},{"pid":"64c7c4ec12a1